Package com.github.dandelion.datatables.core.option.processor

Hierarchy of object for option processors including all generic option processors.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    OptionProcessor
    Super interface for all Option processors.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractOptionProcessor
    Abstract superclass for all Option processors.
    BooleanProcessor
    Processor used for all Boolean parameters.
    EmptyStringProcessor
    Processes the option value as a String and accepts blank values.
    IntegerProcessor
    Processor used for all Integer parameters.
    OptionProcessingContext
    Context in which an Option/value pair is processed.
    StringBuilderProcessor
    Processor used for all String parameters.
    StringProcessor
    Processes the option value as a String but returns null either if the value is blank or null.
